Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那台打字机\N{\rYUANWEN}That typewriter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:54.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,它对我来说太重了\N{\rYUANWEN}It's too heavy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,女士 这座城市正在遭到袭击\N{\rYUANWEN}Ma'am, the city's under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那可不\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯 那就干点事儿 打字机 放上去\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, be useful. The typewriter, up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你得赶紧离开\N{\rYUANWEN}You need to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我的工作室\N{\rYUANWEN}This is my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:08.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在这一个地方待了40年左右\N{\rYUANWEN}Same place for 40 years, give or take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:10.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看 放最上面的架子 麻烦了\N{\rYUANWEN}Look, top shelf, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下士说得对 女士\N{\rYUANWEN}The corporal's right, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这里不安全\N{\rYUANWEN}This location is not secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:19.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们在去舰队司令部的路上 我们可以带你一起去\N{\rYUANWEN}We're on our way to FLEETCOM. We can take you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:23.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那谁来照看我的东西呢\N{\rYUANWEN}And who'll look after all my stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:27.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,女士 这些都不重要\N{\rYUANWEN}Ma'am, all of this doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:33.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是个安德伍德便携机械打字机\N{\rYUANWEN}That's an Underwood standard portable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:34.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,二十世纪的东西\N{\rYUANWEN}Twentieth century.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:37.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来自康涅狄格州哈特福德\N{\rYUANWEN}Hartford, Connecticut
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是在地球上 亲爱的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's Earth, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,它经历了六次战争\N{\rYUANWEN}It's seen six wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:46.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,见识过共产主义 法西斯主义 还有所有介于这两者之间的主义\N{\rYUANWEN}Fought communism, fascism, all the isms in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并且幸存了下来\N{\rYUANWEN}And it survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在 如果这都不重要的话\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, if that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:54.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,星盟马上就到了 女士\N{\rYUANWEN}The Covenant is on the way, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:57.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在人们说话的样子就好像什么都不重要\N{\rYUANWEN}People nowadays talk like nothing matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我们是谁呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Who are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:03.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果什么都不重要 那我们也不重要\N{\rYUANWEN}If nothing matters, then we don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,女士 他们要把这颗星球玻璃化\N{\rYUANWEN}Ma'am, they're gonna glass the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一切都将不复存在 你无法幸存\N{\rYUANWEN}Nothing will survive. You will not survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-女士 你明白吗  -她明白的\N{\rYUANWEN}Ma'am, do you understand? - She understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是什么 你的秘密地牢吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What is this? Your secret dungeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,监禁是次要目的\N{\rYUANWEN}Incarceration is a secondary purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这主要是一个实验\N{\rYUANWEN}It's principally an experimentation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以及审讯场所\N{\rYUANWEN}and interrogation site.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,仅限海军情报局访问\N{\rYUANWEN}ONI access only.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就是地牢呗\N{\rYUANWEN}So, like a dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们越来越近了\N{\rYUANWEN}They're getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:56.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉我 给我讲讲凯斯勒吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell me, what's Kessler like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:58.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他多大了 他大概9岁或者10岁了吧\N{\rYUANWEN}How old is he? He must be 9 or 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:01.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我打赌他崇拜你  -别说了\N{\rYUANWEN}- I bet he worships you. - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当你那么大的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}When you were that age,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:04.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你总是想要溜走\N{\rYUANWEN}you were always trying to slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,爬墙钻洞\N{\rYUANWEN}Climbing, tunneling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想和你谈我儿子的事\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't want to talk to you about my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,父母就是会谈论自己的孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, that's what parents talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,至少别人是这么告诉我的\N{\rYUANWEN}or so I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:13.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有个孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}You had a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:16.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 很自然地 我很想知道\N{\rYUANWEN}So, naturally, I'm curious to know how much of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你对他的影响有多大\N{\rYUANWEN}has found its way into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我感兴趣纯粹是科学方面的原因\N{\rYUANWEN}My interest is purely scientific.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,放屁\N{\rYUANWEN}Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:24.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道我们这是要去哪吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you even know where we're headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯 我当然知道\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我记得\N{\rYUANWEN}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你当时是最积极的那个\N{\rYUANWEN}you were the most driven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,其他人是被招募进来的\N{\rYUANWEN}The others had to be recruited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你是说绑架来的吧  -但你是自愿的\N{\rYUANWEN}Kidnapped. - But you wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从我第一次见到你开始\N{\rYUANWEN}Right from the very first time I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你就想当斯巴达战士\N{\rYUANWEN}You wanted to be a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:44.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我当时6岁  -没错 你当时才6岁\N{\rYUANWEN}- I was 6. - Yes, you were 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你已经知道了自己的目标\N{\rYUANWEN}And you already knew your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\rYUANWEN}So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是个天生的战士\N{\rYUANWEN}You were a born warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-即便在你出了事故之后 你  -我的什么\N{\rYUANWEN}Even after your accident, you- - - My what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:57.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的手臂\N{\rYUANWEN}Your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,放你离开真的很不容易\N{\rYUANWEN}It was very difficult to let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,放我离开吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Let me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:04.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我逃离了你\N{\rYUANWEN}I escaped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我从你手里幸存了\N{\rYUANWEN}I survived you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我拥有了生活\N{\rYUANWEN}I made a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,即便还有阴魂不散的你\N{\rYUANWEN}in spite of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:19.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我看这是一个很好的故事\N{\rYUANWEN}I suppose that's as good a story as any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:32.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是等离子伤\N{\rYUANWEN}Plasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:35.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等离子伤\N{\rYUANWEN}Plasma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-他们来了  -拿着这个\N{\rYUANWEN}They're here. - Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,最好别在背后向我开枪\N{\rYUANWEN}And try not to shoot me in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.11,0:15:42.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这我没法保证\N{\rYUANWEN}No promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,放低身体\N{\rYUANWEN}Stay low!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上 上 上\N{\rYUANWEN}Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-快走 快走  -走 走\N{\rYUANWEN}Go! Go! - Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:05.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们正在从舰队司令部撤退\N{\rYUANWEN}They're evacuating people from FLEETCOM.
